263
00:21:33,592 --> 00:21:35,894
{\an8}When it comes to <i>SHOCK</i>,

264
00:21:38,130 --> 00:21:40,132
{\an8}I doubt I'll be able to keep it up.

265
00:21:40,666 --> 00:21:41,733
{\an8}Probably.

266
00:21:43,835 --> 00:21:46,605
